views.markdown: If you need help with "YoutubeNoAd", you can contact Linus Yang, the developer, via e-mail.
Linus Yang is the maintainer of the package "YoutubeNoAd". Please contact them via email for any questions on this version of the package.
If you found a mistake in the depiction or cannot download the package, you can reach out to the maintainer of the "Gus's Repo" repo, Gus.
